name: TD Active Global Enhanced Dividend ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of TD Active Global Enhanced Dividend ETF (the Fund) is to seek to earn income and generate moderate capital growth Fund investing primarily in dividend-paying equity securities of issuers located anywhere in the world. In seeking to achieve this objective, the Fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies located around the world. Securities are selected through an active fundamental methodology that considers an issuers ability to profitably generate and grow free cash flow, and its efficiency at allocating capital. In seeking to enhance income, the Fund will write covered call options or cash covered put options.
fulldescription: The investment objective of TD Active Global Enhanced Dividend ETF (the Fund) is to seek to earn income and generate moderate capital growth Fund investing primarily in dividend-paying equity securities of issuers located anywhere in the world. In seeking to achieve this objective, the Fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies located around the world. Securities are selected through an active fundamental methodology that considers an issuers ability to profitably generate and grow free cash flow, and its efficiency at allocating capital. In seeking to enhance income, the Fund will write covered call options or cash covered put options. The Fund may also invest in non-dividend-paying companies and hedge any or all foreign currency exposure
